text: Abdallah Mohamed Kamil (عبد الله محمد كامل; born 1936) is a Djiboutian politician. He was the third Prime Minister of Djibouti from 5 February 1978 to 2 October 1978. He was Minister of Foreign Affairs in the first post- independence government."Mar 1978 - Appointment of New Government -Establishment of Diplomatic Relations with West Germany", Keesing's Record of World Events, Volume XXIV, March, 1978 Djibouti, Page 28891. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Djibouti
